/**
 * Burbank, CA — v2 migrated page (T12 batch).
 * Branch: Los Angeles — service_area (per cities.ts; legacy hardcoded
 * Pasadena, but cities.ts SSOT routes Burbank to LA branch via primaryBranch).
 * Content source: legacy burbank.astro (dump body extracted verbatim).
