 * Verbatim contract: every paragraph, FAQ, recent job, review, neighborhood
 * preserved. The "Why Burbank Is Different" Media-City context narrative
 * is rendered via <CustomNarrative>. The "85% First-Visit Fix Rate" trust
 * badge is the v2 default — no override.
